data.description: Gorgeous, move-in condition, freshly painted and in most convenient location.  Recently re-done; the  kitchen features granite counters, 42 inch cabinets and stainless appliances. French doors lead to the sun room overlooking the large, fenced yard. New carpet in living/dining rooms. The ceramic tiled bathrooms have granite sinks and modern vanities. There are 3 large bedrooms on the upper level and one in the basement. There is a family room with built-in bookcases  on the entry level.  Newer windows throughout. Light, bright and beautiful. See it, you won't be disappointed.
